---
layout: listing
title: Practices
description: "Healing participation practices from the grammar of the Codex — embodied ways of engaging in spiritual repair."
tag: Practices
tagClass: tag--practices
sectionSlug: practices
collectionName: practices
permalink: /practices/
---

{# Alpha jump nav #}
{% set letters = collections.practices | uniqueFirstLetters %}
<nav class="alpha-nav" aria-label="Jump to letter">
  {% for letter in letters %}
    <a class="alpha-nav__link" href="#letter-{{ letter }}">{{ letter }}</a>
  {% endfor %}
</nav>

{# Cards grouped by letter — alpha-group__letter spans the full grid width #}
<div class="grid-cards">
  {% for practice in collections.practices %}
    {% set letter = practice.data.title[0] | upper %}
    {% if loop.first or collections.practices[loop.index0 - 1].data.title[0] | upper != letter %}
      <h2 class="alpha-group__letter" id="letter-{{ letter }}">{{ letter }}</h2>
    {% endif %}
    <a href="{{ practice.url | url }}" class="card">
      <span class="tag tag--practices card__tag">Practice</span>
      <h3 class="card__title">{{ practice.data.title }}</h3>
      <p class="card__excerpt">{{ practice.templateContent | excerpt }}</p>
    </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
